data.description:
Welcome to this charming home with great potential located in a desirable neighborhood in Midway ISD and in close proximity to Woodway amenities and White Hall Park. This lovely 3 bedroom (possible 4 bedroom), 2 bath home with two living areas and a heated/cooled sunroom offers plenty of space for you and your loved ones to make lasting memories. Situated on a large corner lot, this property offers the perfect blend of privacy and room to grow.

The kitchen features a gas stove, dishwasher, and refrigerator, as well as an eat at bar.  Enjoy a warm fire in the gas fireplace located in the enclosed sunroom.

One of the standout features of this property is the expansive lot with rear entry garage and privacy fenced back yard. Imagine the possibilities that await in the generous outdoor space. Ample space to add a pool if so desired.  Whether you envision a lush garden, a tranquil retreat, or a play area, there's room for it all. Embrace the potential to create your own oasis and take advantage of the open canvas that this large lot provides. The large storage building, refrigerator, washing machine, and firepit convey.

New roof. 

Don't miss out on the chance to create your own story in this home. Schedule a showing today and let your imagination run wild!
